article-magazine/.highlight/who-killed-palestinian-american-teen-mohammad-khdour/0000018d-d7d1-db8c-a38d-dffd81340000</guid></item><item><title>以色列必须释放人质并离开加沙。但内塔尼亚胡不会去那里</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-must-get-the-hostages-freed-and-leave-gaza-but-netanyahu-isnt-going-there/0000018d-d704-df79-a5cd-f73eebb90000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 18:32:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-must-get-the-hostages-freed-and-leave-gaza-but-netanyahu-isnt-going-there/0000018d-d704-df79-a5cd-f73eebb90000</guid></item><item><title>美国称约旦河西岸定居点非法，扭转特朗普时代的“蓬佩奥主义”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-23/ty-article/.premium/u-s-effectively-reverses-pompeo-doctrine-on-legality-of-west-bank-settlements/0000018d-d707-db8c-a38d-df7fd4e00000</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯表示，以色列宣布修建新的定居点令人“失望”，并补充说，这些“对实现持久和平起反作用”</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 18:21:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-23/ty-article/.premium/u-s-effectively-reverses-pompeo-doctrine-on-legality-of-west-bank-settlements/0000018d-d707-db8c-a38d-df7fd4e00000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的内容 – 第 140 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-140/0000018d-d6ea-d47b-a1af-defe5f170000</link><description>以色列宣布计划建造数千套住房后，拜登政府宣布约旦河西岸定居点“不符合国际法” ■ 总理内塔尼亚胡公布加沙“后天”计划 ■ 以色列谈判代表正在巴黎参加旨在确保人质获释的峰会停火协议 哈马斯卫生部：加沙有 70 万名儿童营养不良、脱水 战争 140 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 18:01:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-140/0000018d-d6ea-d47b-a1af-defe5f170000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦领导层的后阿巴斯时代计划正在艰难实施</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-23/ty-article/.premium/pales