f7-a3ff-d2fd75b80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列代表团启程前往巴黎参加人质谈判；消息人士称，双方计划下个月起草协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/pm-netanyahu-sends-team-to-paris-for-hostage-talks-parties-want-draft-by-march/0000018d-d26d-df79-a5cd-f27f1c640000</link><description>以色列官员认为，作为协议的一部分，哈马斯可能会在以色列释放巴勒斯坦囚犯的数量和身份方面表现出更大的灵活性，但预计该组织将继续要求结束战斗</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 20:50:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/pm-netanyahu-sends-team-to-paris-for-hostage-talks-parties-want-draft-by-march/0000018d-d26d-df79-a5cd-f27f1c640000</guid></item></channel></rss>